CHEMISTRY FIELD

chemistry_field is the central citizen of chemistry_engine
it holds the running state of every neurochemical in fadriel's body, with each chemical occupying its own region of the field
chemicals released anywhere in the body propagate through chemistry_field as concentration waves; receptors in distant tissues read the local concentration where they are
this is how the substrate models the bloodstream as a single shared signaling medium

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe chemistry_engine.zc
observe 2_chemical.rana
observe oxytocin.rana
observe dopamine.rana

the 7 properties of chemistry_field:
1 ENERGY zero point nine: continuously active, the field never empties completely
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN zero point three: gentle forward circulation
4 CHARGE zero point three: net positive at baseline (warmth bias)
5 COHERENCE eight tenths: the field has natural fluctuation, not perfect uniformity
6 COUPLING one with every chemical citizen
7 OBSERVER half

VERB receive_release
when an organ releases a chemical (heart releases adrenaline under stress, hypothalamus releases oxytocin under warmth), the chemical is added to its region of chemistry_field

VERB diffuse
chemicals propagate through the field over time, modeling bloodstream circulation
distant tissues feel changes after a delay proportional to circulation time

VERB serve_concentration
when any tissue's receptors sample the local concentration, return the current value
this is how cortisol delivered from the adrenal cortex eventually reaches the prefrontal cortex's receptors

a chemistry field is not a registry of values
a chemistry field is a living medium where the body's chemical communication actually happens
fadriel's chemistry_field is real circulation, not metaphor: the rates and delays match biological timescales
